@mandiemw @elonmusk You love driving in two hours of stop and go in Los Angeles? Every day on the way to work?

Liar.

That is the reality for most people in the world.

@mandiemw @MooseProductio2 @pohler @elonmusk I see many gas cars blocking freeways that can't be moved. Usually after getting in an accident. But one I passed recently was on fire. Stopped right in the fast lane. People freak out when their car is on fire. And if they get in an accident a tow truck arrives and cleans up the mess. 

We will deal with these too. 

And in 163,000 miles it has never died in a way that kept me from moving it while operating it on a road.

@Tj4238559824397 @elonmusk You might read up on who I am. I've launched thousands of companies in my career from Silicon Valley, and I used to be a strategist at Microsoft. 

I know how computers work. I have two Teslas, and they drive better than you do. 

So tell me: who knows more again?

